Body:
Description: Hi team,

We are working on a tender document and one of the questions is: Blocking and identifying hacking devices (Flipper Zero, raspberry pi)

Can we block these devices?

Thank you
Stefania
To do: Speak with Cristian to raise ADO

00417887 - Compilation of questions raised by TSMC response:

We are not able to control USB devices that use the UART protocol to communicate. We try to block them but we are unable because macOS ensures the device can be used by applications.
Next Steps Updated: Checking with Robert Z.
